<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">tribhu</hi>vaṉa cakkiravaṟttikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>vikkiramacOḻa tE
<lb n="2" break="no"/>vaṟkku yāṇṭu <num value="14"><g type="numeral">10</g> 4</num> vatu <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi><supplied reason="omitted">ya</supplied>ciṅka vaḷanāṭ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭupperuvayal nāṭṭut tiruvēṅkai vāyilāṇ
<lb n="4"/>ṭār cittiraittirunāḷukkuk kūttāṭukaikku cān
<lb n="5" break="no"/>tik kūttāṭukiṟa Ēḻunāṭṭu naṅkaikku kūttāṭukaik
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kku viṭṭa nilamāvatu tēvartānam tippaiyā vayalu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>m kuḷamum vaḷaiyil cuṟṟum Inta Ēḻunā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭṭu naṅkaikku viṭṭa Innilam koṟṟukku <unclear>kācukkum</unclear>
<lb n="9"/>Ivaṉ Innilaṅkoṇṭu Ittirunāḷukku Āṭak
<lb n="10" break="no"/>kaṭava kūttu Oṉpatum Āṭuvāḷākavum viḷai
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yāta Āṇṭu Āṭiṉa kūttukku koṟṟu viṭuvatā
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ka Innilam <unclear>viṭṭōm</unclear> peruvayal nāṭṭu nāṭ
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṭōmum <hi rend="grantha">māheśvara</hi>rum paṉ <hi rend="grantha">māheśvara rakṣai</hi> 
</p>

